---
const DOWNLOAD_URL =
  'https://github.com/junhyung-space/clix/releases/latest/download/clix.dmg';
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center
         px-8 pb-20 pt-24 text-center overflow-hidden"
  style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 65% at 50% -10%, rgba(30,64,175,0.4) 0%, transparent 65%), radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 85% 90%, rgba(14,165,233,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%), #0a0e1a;"
>
  <!-- App Icon -->
  <img
    src="/icon.png"
    alt="CLIX App Icon"
    class="w-24 h-24 rounded-[22px] mb-9"
    style="box-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(14,165,233,0.22), 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);"
  />

  <!-- Headline -->
  <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-[1.02] mb-6">
    <span class="grad-text" data-i18n="hero.headline1">AI 시대를 위해</span>
    <br />
    <span class="grad-text" data-i18n="hero.headline2">새로 만든 SSH</span>
  </h1>

  <!-- Sub -->
  <p
    class="text-lg text-text-secondary max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-12"
    data-i18n="hero.sub"
  >
    Claude Code, Codex, Gemini CLI와 함께 일하는 개발자를 위한 터미널
  </p>

  <!-- AI Tool Badges -->
  <div class="flex gap-2.5 justify-center mb-12 flex-wrap">
    {[
      { name: 'Claude Code', color: '#f97316' },
      { name: 'Codex', color: '#8b5cf6' },
      { name: 'Gemini CLI', color: '#06b6d4' },
    ].map(({ name, color }) => (
      <div
        class="flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.08]
               rounded-lg px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs text-text-muted"
      >
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={`background:${color}`}></span>
        {name}
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <a
    href={DOWNLOAD_URL}
    class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white
           text-base font-bold px-9 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 mb-5"
    data-i18n="hero.cta"
  >
    macOS용 다운로드 — 무료
  </a>

  <!-- Meta -->
  <p
    class="text-xs text-text-darkest"
    data-i18n="hero.meta"
  >
    macOS 14.0 Sonoma 이상 · Apple Silicon & Intel
  </p>
</section>
